Package: iitm-login-manager
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Shriman <shrimansoft@gmail.com>
Installed-Size: 96
Depends: python3-bs4, python3-cryptography (>= 3.4.0), python3-gi, python3-keyring, python3-requests, python3-schedule, python3:any, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1, gir1.2-notify-0.7
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/shrimansoft/iitm-login-manager
Description: Automated login system for IIT Madras network access
 IITM Login Manager is a comprehensive automation tool designed specifically
 for IIT Madras students and staff to streamline network access. It provides
 both command-line and graphical interfaces for managing internet connectivity.
 .
 Key features include:
  * Automated login to IITM network with secure credential storage
  * System tray application with real-time status monitoring
  * Scheduled login attempts (daily/twice daily)
  * Desktop notifications for login events
  * Command-line interface for scripting and automation
  * Cross-platform compatibility with Linux desktop environments
 .
 The application uses secure keyring storage for credentials and provides
 a user-friendly setup process for first-time configuration.
